Package edu.missouri.geom

This package defines a collection of geometrical objects useful for coverage path planning and UAV trajectory planning.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Angle
    A geometry component corresponding to a three-point angle.
    Coordinate  
    csvCreate  
    Line
    A geometric object representing a line segment, ray, or infinite line.
    Point
    An n-dimensional Cartesian point.
    Polygon
    A two-dimensional n-gon.
    PolygonFactory
    PolygonFactory creates some useful polygons which define regions with important characteristics for coverage problems.
    Util
    A static collection of useful methods.
